   potential energy curves within the framework of the Jenc reduced
   potential energy curve (RPC) approach. In turn, the resulting potential
   energy curves are used to determine the radial functions describing the
   spin-rotation and hyperfine energy patterns of the spin-rovibrational
   energy levels by morphing/fitting their ab initio/empirical
